PrecisOrder authorizing the three Deputy Directors of Investigation and Research, namely Mr. Harry S. Chandler, Ms. Rachel Larabie-Lesieur and Mr. Gilles Ménard, to exercise the powers and perform the duties of the Acting Director of Investigation and Research whenever the Acting Director is absent or unable to do so.
